(63710, 141235, 5618, 8, '熱戀', '活著久了誰都難免覺得想死', '2013-07-23 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 4, '我曾經熱戀過\n也曾經驗過「天堂」\n喔，那燃燒的火焰\n你深陷的雙眼\n\n如今走在空曠的大道上\n你自己一個人\n享受，翻著舊的書\n\n不要讓我悲傷\n不要讓我再擔心你了\n我一直想著你的臉孔\n\n那些謠言乏味的像遠山的白色雲朵\n離我好遠，也霎時不見了足跡\n\n無盡的生命呀\n活著久了誰都難免覺得想死\n\n無盡的生命呀\n', '', 288, '', '邱比', '邱比', 'Chiu-Pi', 'Chiu-Pi / Gallery', '', 1, 0, 1, '2013-05-18 22:50:07', '2013-12-25 00:34:09', '2013-12-25 00:34:09'),
(63711, 182598, 0, 1, 'Kaleidoscope_萬花筒', '世界是萬花筒，\n你怎麼在你的世界裡，將它\n著色、上漆；\n又怎麼在人生的高速公路上，\n走出自己想要的花色與質感...\n這都在於\n你，不是嗎？\n造物主把鑰匙交到了你的手裡\n不妨開個敞蓬車\n去兜個風吧。', '2013-03-02 00:00:00', 2000, 1, 1, 4, 'Stop and stare at the world, you''ll find\nIt''s such a kaleidoscope of various style\nIt takes you to a highway waiting for a drive\nKey''s on your hand come on and have your own ride\nDon''t stand still waiting, come on add some colour to\nyour masterpiece, oh lift your hand now\nKeep on painting, add some colour, add some colour to\nyour masterpiece, ur huh ur huh\nWake up, dude, don''t keep stick to your bed, I\nsee you waste your fun time like Coke overnight\nGrab my arm, twist your body and wear your smile\ncuz'' world''s a kaleidoscope of various style\nAwhhh, Mama says''Little Johnny you''ve enjoy the great day,\ndinner''s ready don''t you wanna go back inside?''\n''No?'' ''No!''\n(I''ve still got whole bunch all lot of things to do out there, mama\nI''m changing the world)', 'Stop and stare at the world, you''ll find\nIt''s such a kaleidoscope of various style\nIt takes you to a highway waiting for a drive\nKey''s on your hand come on and have your own ride\nDon''t stand still waiting, come on add some colour to\nyour masterpiece, oh lift your hand now\nKeep on painting, add some colour, add some colour to\nyour masterpiece, ur huh ur huh\nWake up, dude, don''t keep stick to your bed, I\nsee you waste your fun time like Coke overnight\nGrab my arm, twist your body and wear your smile\ncuz'' world''s a kaleidoscope of various style\nAwhhh, Mama says''Little Johnny you''ve enjoy the great day,\ndinner''s ready don''t you wanna go back inside?''\n''No?'' ''No!''\n(I''ve still got whole bunch all lot of things to do out there, mama\nI''m changing the world)', 182, '', '裘詠靖', '裘詠靖', '李宏俊', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-05-18 23:16:59', '2015-03-12 14:00:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
